data.description: ***We have received multiple offers  on 12 E WASHINGTON STREET, FLEETWOOD. We are requesting highest and best offers to be submitted by 12 noon on Sunday 4/21/24.***  Welcome to beautiful 12 E Washington Street located in the heart of Fleetwood in the Fleetwood School District. This 3 story brick home is full of both character and charm and has been meticulously maintained by the current  owners. Open the door and prepare to fall in love as the newer LVP flooring and soaring ceilings lead you into a perfect flowing floor plan. Spacious Foyer with plenty of room for seating. Large living room with original stained glass windows. Dining room with built in granite table and new light fixture. The white kitchen has a gorgeous tile backsplash, plenty of cabinets/countertops and black appliances which all remain with the home. Convenient main floor updated 1/2 bath. The second level has a primary bedroom with an oversized walk-in-closet. 2 additional generous sized private bedrooms both with ample closet space. Updated full bathroom with whirlpool tub/shower combo. The attic has been finished into room for an additional bedroom or living space. A patio overlooks a fenced in flat back yard with hot tub. Plenty of space for yard tools and toys in the shed. Off street parking for at least 4 cars. Peace of mind is yours with natural gas heat and a brand new central air unit. Close proximity to schools, shopping and major highways. You will love to call this your Home Sweet Home
